          </div>
          <div class="p-5 flex flex-col flex-1 gap-4">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-text-main dark:text-white">Corrugated Boxes</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mt-1">Durable, multi-wall boxes designed for safe transport of heavy industrial goods.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-auto pt-4 border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-xs font-medium text-gray-400">Min. Order: 50 units</span>
              <a href="/products/cardboard" class="rounded-lg bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 hover:bg-primary hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors">
                View Details
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark shadow-sm border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="relative w-full aspect-[4/3] bg-gray-100">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center" style='background-image: url("https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAAIermlivl2_DMSJYlvoSHeAMElUY9Ld72lnS-Kid8Z1yuK_ztLaiGU0jNaLPpmOCDFsNyANsRlSuczy5K85L5a-YUIoqI7-DZgiuHFwEQWKtM1VTrmX6l54nbyhpk1ZhXC-qWpTHZNnsMJzZpDBr0howqbGmx0bopuFpiDDyEI8vpJCBW12p0td7hIkkuVepBkBUPfdXwHf6krVUGeOVflK1cccdQUeuH6VmIEas1T2o9Qj1Nzw7tDRJA0KOjs9YpCc9NVAkunWzn");'></div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-5 flex flex-col flex-1 gap-4">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-text-main dark:text-white">Industrial Stretch Film</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mt-1">High-quality, puncture-resistant film for load stability and pallet security.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-auto pt-4 border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-xs font-medium text-gray-400">Min. Order: 10 rolls</span>
              <a href="/products/plastic-wrap" class="rounded-lg bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 hover:bg-primary hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors">
                View Details
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark shadow-sm border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="relative w-full aspect-[4/3] bg-gray-100">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center" style='background-image: url("https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBt0hCcxtDB6pmwG3GTZnnkGEnwxRziU1uknBNjeglsUI3EDXh96bcsQuE6VpbP0aAH-4ecgTo60u7vcQfL-lEqTmmKCzuEJyhl567aeXQ5mEMpo86WBCFNZ6FrX7VW9RgFe0YHZmf64-tW2RZWzTc3Cw0X8o86j9sv7Q54t_8BdLEoUpKAw7Las-RBj_JCcTm0LWmSHqd3GiozIIMF9OHjdr4aL9LOY0bZwQmbFzdqos4yZYSDDAdZOEndz_Gx9wu2suLNBM02yAcM");'></div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-5 flex flex-col flex-1 gap-4">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-text-main dark:text-white">Custom Pallets</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mt-1">Standard and custom-sized wooden and plastic pallets treated for export.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-auto pt-4 border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-xs font-medium text-gray-400">Custom Dimensions</span>
              <a href="/products/custom" class="rounded-lg bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 hover:bg-primary hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors">
                View Details
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-900 text-white rounded-t-[2rem] mx-2 lg:mx-4 mb-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black tracking-tight mb-6">Ready to optimize your supply chain?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Get a personalized quote for your business today. Our team is ready to help you find the perfect packaging solution.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="w-full sm:w-auto h-12 px-8 rounded-sm bg-primary text-gray-900 font-bold hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors inline-flex items-center justify-center">
